race.comment: NEVERENOUGHLEGO (2) has placed in half of his 10 runs and is long overdue for a win. Freshened since finishing runner-up this trip at Tatura in the latest when tried to lead throughout and was grabbed in the last stride. Take catching again. DAISY DUCK (7) resumed from a long break at Sandown Hillside and wasn't far away. Fitter and this is easier. Expected to feature. SHARE THE STARS (8) is fitter for two runs back and ran well at both. Third in a richer maiden at Cranbourne last time and should appreciate the longer journey now. CRESPIANO (1) resumes and is well placed over this longer journey fresh. Placed 2/2 at the trip and 2/2 when fresh-up. ETCHED IN BLUE (11) was well off best last time but previous figures have him right in this.
